===Etymology===
{{etyl|ang}} {{term|writan|wrītan|lang=ang}}, from {{proto|Germanic|writan}}, possibly from ''rītsan'', ''rīzan'', meaning ''to scratch'' or ''mark''. Cognate with Dutch {{term|rijten|lang=nl}}, German {{term|ritzen|lang=de}}, Norwegian {{term|rita|lang=no}}

